        <updateDate>2020-05-05T17:03:50Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Veterans Cemetery Grants Improvement Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases to $10 million (currently $5 million) the maximum amount the Department of Veterans Affairs may grant in a fiscal year to states and tribal organizations for operating and maintaining veterans' cemeteries.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
